msgid "# Additional Configuration"
msgstr "# 附加配置"

msgid ""
"Additional configuration is a mechanism provided by vLLM to allow plugins to"
" control internal behavior by themselves. VLLM Ascend uses this mechanism to"
" make the project more flexible."
msgstr "附加配置是 vLLM 提供的一种机制，允许插件自行控制内部行为。VLLM Ascend 利用此机制使项目更加灵活。"

msgid "## Migration Guide"
msgstr "## 迁移指南"

msgid ""
"Starting from [PR #9064](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/pull/9064), vLLM Ascend is migrating **10 environment variables** to "
"`--additional-config`."
msgstr ""
"从 [PR #9064](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/9064) 开始，VLLM "
"Ascend 正在将 **10 个环境变量** 迁移至 `--additional-config`。"

msgid "### Important Notice"
msgstr "### 重要提示"

msgid ""
"- **Current Support**: Both environment variables and `--additional-config` are supported during the transition period\n"
"- **Recommendation**: Use `--additional-config` for new deployments and migrate existing configurations\n"
"- **Future Plan**: Environment variables will be **removed** in a future release; only `--additional-config` will be supported"
msgstr ""
"- **当前支持**：过渡期内环境变量和 `--additional-config` 均受支持\n"
"- **建议**：新部署请使用 `--additional-config`，并迁移现有配置\n"
"- **未来计划**：环境变量将在未来版本中**移除**，仅支持 `--additional-config`"

msgid "### Quick Reference"
msgstr "### 快速参考"

msgid "### Example Migration"
msgstr "### 迁移示例"

msgid "**Before (environment variable):**"
msgstr "**之前（环境变量）：**"

msgid "**After (additional-config):**"
msgstr "**之后（附加配置）：**"

