msgstr "无论是在线模式还是离线模式，用户都可以使用附加配置。以 Qwen3 为例："

msgid "**Online mode**:"
msgstr "**在线模式**："

msgid "**Offline mode**:"
msgstr "**离线模式**："

msgid "### Configuration options"
msgstr "### 配置选项"

msgid ""
"The following table lists additional configuration options available in vLLM"
" Ascend:"
msgstr "下表列出了 vLLM Ascend 中可用的附加配置选项："

msgid "The details of each configuration option are as follows:"
msgstr "每个配置选项的详细信息如下："

msgid "**xlite_graph_config**"
msgstr "**xlite_graph_config**"

msgid "**weight_prefetch_config**"
msgstr "**weight_prefetch_config**"

msgid "**finegrained_tp_config**"
msgstr "**finegrained_tp_config**"

msgid "**ascend_compilation_config**"
msgstr "**ascend_compilation_config**"

msgid "**eplb_config**"
msgstr "**eplb_config**"

msgid "**profiling_chunk_config**"
msgstr "**profiling_chunk_config**"

msgid "**rejection_sampler_config**"
msgstr "**rejection_sampler_config**"

msgid ""
"> **Note**: Both block verify and entropy verify improve speculative "
"decoding performance (higher acceptance rate, lower latency) at the cost of "
"reduced sampling precision. A larger `posterior_alpha` makes the adjustment "
"more aggressive — it further lowers the acceptance threshold for high-"
"entropy tokens, improving throughput but degrading output quality. Users "
"should tune these parameters based on their specific model weights and "
"application scenario to find the right trade-off between performance and "
"precision."
msgstr ""
"> **注意**：块验证和熵验证都能提升投机解码性能（更高的接受率、更低的延迟），但代价是降低采样精度。`posterior_alpha` "
"值越大，调整越激进——它会进一步降低高熵 token "
"的接受阈值，从而提高吞吐量但降低输出质量。用户应根据具体的模型权重和应用场景调整这些参数，以在性能和精度之间找到合适的平衡点。"

