"|"

msgid ""
"| `eplb_config`                       | dict | `{}`    | Configuration "
"options for eplb |"
msgstr "| `eplb_config`                       | dict | `{}`    | eplb 的配置选项 |"

msgid ""
"| `refresh`                           | bool | `false` | Whether to refresh "
"global Ascend configuration content. This is usually used by rlhf or ut/e2e "
"test case. |"
msgstr ""
"| `refresh`                           | bool | `false` | 是否刷新全局 Ascend "
"配置内容。通常用于 rlhf 或 ut/e2e 测试用例。 |"

msgid ""
"| `dump_config`                       | dict | `None`  | Inline msprobe dump"
" configuration. vLLM-Ascend will materialize it to a temporary JSON file and"
" pass that file to the debugger. |"
msgstr ""
"| `dump_config`                       | dict | `None`  | 内联的 msprobe dump "
"配置。vLLM-Ascend 会将其物化为一个临时 JSON 文件，并将该文件传递给调试器。 |"

msgid ""
"| `dump_config_path`                  | str  | `None`  | Configuration file "
"path for msprobe dump (compatible legacy option)."
"                                      |"
msgstr ""
"| `dump_config_path`                  | str  | `None`  | msprobe dump "
"的配置文件路径（兼容的旧选项）。"
"                                                             |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_async_exponential`          | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"asynchronous exponential overlap. To enable asynchronous exponential, set "
"this config to True.        |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_async_exponential`          | bool | `False` | "
"是否启用异步指数重叠。要启用异步指数，请将此配置设置为 True。"
"                                             |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_shared_expert_dp`           | bool | `False` | When the expert is "
"shared in DP, it delivers better performance but consumes more memory. "
"Currently only DeepSeek series models are supported. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_shared_expert_dp`           | bool | `False` | 当专家在 DP "
"中共享时，性能更好但内存消耗更大。目前仅支持 DeepSeek 系列模型。 |"

msgid ""
"| `multistream_overlap_shared_expert` | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"multi-stream shared expert. This option only takes effect on MoE models with"
" shared experts. |"
msgstr ""
"| `multistream_overlap_shared_expert` | bool | `False` | "
"是否启用多流共享专家。此选项仅对具有共享专家的 MoE 模型生效。 |"

msgid ""
"| `multistream_overlap_gate`          | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"multi-stream overlap gate. This option only takes effect on MoE models with "
"shared experts.  |"
msgstr ""
"| `multistream_overlap_gate`          | bool | `False` | "
"是否启用多流重叠门控。此选项仅对具有共享专家的 MoE 模型生效。 |"

msgid ""
"| `recompute_scheduler_enable`        | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"the recompute scheduler. **Only valid on PD-disaggregated D nodes** "
"(`kv_role` is `kv_consumer`). **Do not enable on P nodes or in PD-mixed "
"mode** (no `kv_transfer_config`, `kv_role` is `kv_producer`, or `kv_role` is"
" `kv_both`); startup will fail with a clear error. |"
msgstr ""
"| `recompute_scheduler_enable`        | bool | `False` | 是否启用重计算调度器。**仅在 PD "
"分离的 D 节点上有效**（`kv_role` 为 `kv_consumer`）。**请勿在 P 节点或 PD 混合模式下启用**（无 "
"`kv_transfer_config`，`kv_role` 为 `kv_producer`，或 `kv_role` 为 "
"`kv_both`）；启动将失败并显示明确的错误信息。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_cpu_binding`                | bool | `True`  | Enables Ascend-"
"native CPU binding on ARM servers. Set to `False` to disable. See [CPU "
"Binding](../feature_guide/cpu_binding.md). |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_cpu_binding`                | bool | `True`  | 在 ARM 服务器上启用 Ascend"
" 原生 CPU 绑定。设置为 `False` 以禁用。请参阅 [CPU 绑定](../feature_guide/cpu_binding.md)。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_sleep_mode_extra_cleanup`   | bool | `False` | Enables extra "
"sleep-mode cleanup for RL workloads, including HCCL process-group release "
"and ACL graph workspace cleanup. Disabled by default because wakeup may need"
" to restore HCCL and recapture ACL graphs. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_sleep_mode_extra_cleanup`   | bool | `False` | 为 RL "
"工作负载启用额外的睡眠模式清理，包括 HCCL 进程组释放和 ACL 图工作空间清理。默认禁用，因为唤醒可能需要恢复 HCCL 并重新捕获 ACL 图。"
" |"

msgid ""
"| `SLO_limits_for_dynamic_batch`      | int  | `-1`    | SLO limits for "
"dynamic batch. This is new scheduler to support dynamic batch feature"
"                            |"
msgstr ""
"| `SLO_limits_for_dynamic_batch`      | int  | `-1`    | 动态批次的 SLO "
"限制。这是一个支持动态批次特性的新调度器。                                                    |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_npugraph_ex`                | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"npugraph_ex graph mode."
"                                                                 |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_npugraph_ex`                | bool | `False` | 是否启用 npugraph_ex "
"图模式。"
"                                                                             "
"|"

msgid ""
"| `pa_shape_list`                     | list | `[]`    | The custom shape "
"list of page attention ops."
"                                                              |"
msgstr ""
"| `pa_shape_list`                     | list | `[]`    | page attention "
"算子的自定义形状列表。"
"                                                                     |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_kv_nz`                      | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"KV cache NZ layout. This option only takes effects on models using MLA "
"(e.g., DeepSeek).                                      |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_kv_nz`                      | bool | `False` | 是否启用 KV 缓存 NZ "
"布局。此选项仅对使用 MLA 的模型（例如 DeepSeek）生效。                                |"

msgid ""
"| `layer_sharding`                    | dict | `{}`    | Configuration "
"options for Layer Sharding Linear. Layer Sharding can only be enabled in PD-"
"disaggregated's P node. |"
msgstr ""
"| `layer_sharding`                    | dict | `{}`    | Layer Sharding "
"Linear 的配置选项。Layer Sharding 只能在 PD 分离的 P 节点上启用。                            |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_sparse_c8`                  | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"KV cache C8 in DSA models (e.g., DeepSeek V3.2 and GLM5). Not supported on "
"Ascend 950 devices now |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_sparse_c8`                  | bool | `False` | 是否在 DSA 模型（例如 "
"DeepSeek V3.2 和 GLM5）中启用 KV 缓存 C8。目前不支持 Ascend 950 设备。              |"

msgid ""
"| `c8_enable_reshape_optim`           | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"StoreKVBlock operator achieves acceleration under the C8 feature (this means"
" that enable_sparse_c8 needs to be enabled). In the PD separation scenario, "
"only the P node is enabled. |"
msgstr ""
"| `c8_enable_reshape_optim`           | bool | `False` | 是否启用 StoreKVBlock "
"算子在 C8 特性下实现加速（这意味着需要启用 enable_sparse_c8）。在 PD 分离场景中，仅 P 节点启用。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_mc2_hierarchy_comm`         | bool | `False` | Enable "
"dispatch/combine op inter-node communication by ROCE. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_mc2_hierarchy_comm`         | bool | `False` | 通过 ROCE 启用 "
"dispatch/combine 算子的节点间通信。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_prefill_mc2`                | bool | `False` | Whether to reserve "
"mc2_token_capacity for prefill batches. When enabled, "
"`max_num_batched_tokens` is used to calculate the mc2_token_capacity instead"
" of the decode-only capacity. In this scenario, the recommended maximum "
"value of `max_num_batched_tokens` is `tp_size * 512`. This is a temporary "
"switch; once MC2 operators are complete for all scenarios, this switch will "
"be removed and MC2 will be enabled by default. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_prefill_mc2`                | bool | `False` | 是否为预填充批次预留 "
"mc2_token_capacity。启用后，将使用 `max_num_batched_tokens` 而非仅解码容量来计算 "
"mc2_token_capacity。在此场景下，`max_num_batched_tokens` 的推荐最大值为 `tp_size * "
"512`。这是一个临时开关；一旦 MC2 算子在所有场景下完备，此开关将被移除，MC2 将默认启用。 |"

msgid ""
"| `mega_moe_max_tokens`               | int  | `65536` | Per-rank token "
"capacity after dispatch in the mega moe (dispatch_ffn_combine) fused "
"operator. When load imbalance causes a rank to receive more tokens than this"
" limit, the excess tokens are dropped and skipped from computation, "
"degrading accuracy. Do not set this too large: workspace memory scales "
"linearly with this value. |"
msgstr ""
"| `mega_moe_max_tokens`               | int  | `65536` | 在 mega "
"moe（dispatch_ffn_combine）融合算子中，每个 rank 在分发后的 token 容量。当负载不均衡导致某个 rank 接收的 "
"token 超过此限制时，多余的 token 将被丢弃并跳过计算，从而降低精度。请勿将此值设置过大：工作空间内存与此值呈线性增长。 |"

msgid ""
"| `profiling_chunk_config`            | dict | `{}`    | Configuration "
"options for dynamic chunked pipeline parallel. See [Dynamic Chunked Pipeline"
" Parallel](../feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md) for details."
" |"
msgstr ""
"| `profiling_chunk_config`            | dict | `{}`    | "
"动态分块流水线并行的配置选项。详情请参见[动态分块流水线并行](../feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md)。"
" |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_balance_scheduling`         | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"balance scheduling. Can also be configured via the "
"`VLLM_ASCEND_BALANCE_SCHEDULING` environment variable during the migration "
"period. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_balance_scheduling`         | bool | `False` | "
"是否启用均衡调度。在迁移期间，也可以通过 `VLLM_ASCEND_BALANCE_SCHEDULING` 环境变量进行配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_flashcomm1`                 | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"FlashComm1 optimization. Can also be configured via the "
"`VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1` environment variable during the migration "
"period. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_flashcomm1`                 | bool | `False` | 是否启用 FlashComm1 "
"优化。在迁移期间，也可以通过 `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1` 环境变量进行配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_matmul_allreduce`           | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"matmul allreduce optimization. Can also be configured via the "
"`VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_MATMUL_ALLREDUCE` environment variable during the "
"migration period. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_matmul_allreduce`           | bool | `False` | 是否启用 matmul "
"allreduce 优化。在迁移期间，也可以通过 `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_MATMUL_ALLREDUCE` 环境变量进行配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| `flashcomm2_parallel_size`          | int  | `0`     | FlashComm2 parallel"
" size. Can also be configured via the `VLLM_ASCEND_FLASHCOMM2_PARALLEL_SIZE`"
" environment variable during the migration period. |"
msgstr ""
"| `flashcomm2_parallel_size`          | int  | `0`     | FlashComm2 "
"并行大小。在迁移期间，也可以通过 `VLLM_ASCEND_FLASHCOMM2_PARALLEL_SIZE` 环境变量进行配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| `msmonitor_use_daemon`              | bool | `False` | Whether to use "
"daemon mode for msmonitor. Can also be configured via the "
"`MSMONITOR_USE_DAEMON` environment variable during the migration period. |"
msgstr ""
"| `msmonitor_use_daemon`              | bool | `False` | 是否为 msmonitor "
"使用守护进程模式。在迁移期间，也可以通过 `MSMONITOR_USE_DAEMON` 环境变量进行配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_mlapo`                      | bool | `True`  | Whether to enable "
"MLAPO (Model Layer-wise Adaptive Parallel Optimization). Can also be "
"configured via the `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_MLAPO` environment variable during "
"the migration period. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_mlapo`                      | bool | `True`  | 是否启用 "
"MLAPO（模型逐层自适应并行优化）。在迁移期间，也可以通过 `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_MLAPO` 环境变量进行配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| `weight_nz_mode`                    | int  | `1`     | Weight NZ mode. Can"
" also be configured via the `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_NZ` environment variable "
"during the migration period. |"
msgstr ""
"| `weight_nz_mode`                    | int  | `1`     | 权重 NZ "
"模式。在迁移期间，也可以通过 `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_NZ` 环境变量进行配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_context_parallel`           | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"context parallelism. Can also be configured via the "
"`VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_CONTEXT_PARALLEL` environment variable during the "
"migration period. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_context_parallel`           | bool | `False` | "
"是否启用上下文并行。在迁移期间，也可以通过 `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_CONTEXT_PARALLEL` 环境变量进行配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_fused_mc2`                  | int  | `0`     | Fused MC2 "
"configuration. Can also be configured via the `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FUSED_MC2`"
" environment variable during the migration period. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_fused_mc2`                  | int  | `0`     | 融合 MC2 "
"配置。在迁移期间，也可以通过 `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FUSED_MC2` 环境变量进行配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_transpose_kv_cache_by_block`| bool | `True`  | Whether to enable "
"transpose KV cache by block. Can also be configured via the "
"`VLLM_ASCEND_FUSION_OP_TRANSPOSE_KV_CACHE_BY_BLOCK` environment variable "
"during the migration period. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_transpose_kv_cache_by_block`| bool | `True`  | 是否启用按块转置 KV "
"缓存。在迁移期间，也可以通过 `VLLM_ASCEND_FUSION_OP_TRANSPOSE_KV_CACHE_BY_BLOCK` 环境变量进行配置。"
" |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_dsa_cp`                     | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"dsa_cp for DeepSeek V3.2, DeepSeek V4, and other models with the same "
"architecture. This feature depends on FLASHCOMM1. Please ensure that "
"FLASHCOMM1 is enabled before enabling this feature.|"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_dsa_cp`                     | bool | `False` | 是否为 DeepSeek "
"V3.2、DeepSeek V4 及其他相同架构的模型启用 dsa_cp。此功能依赖于 FLASHCOMM1。请在启用此功能前确保 FLASHCOMM1"
" 已启用。|"

msgid ""
"| `rejection_sampler_config`          | dict | `{}`    | Configuration "
"options for rejection sampler (block verify and entropy verify). |"
msgstr ""
"| `rejection_sampler_config`          | dict | `{}`    | "
"拒绝采样器（块验证和熵验证）的配置选项。 |"

msgid ""
"| `multistream_dsv4_dsa_overlap`      | bool | `True`  | Whether to enable "
"dsa multi-stream overlap for DeepSeek V4.  |"
msgstr ""
"| `multistream_dsv4_dsa_overlap`      | bool | `True`  | 是否为 DeepSeek V4 启用 "
"dsa 多流重叠。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enabled` | bool | `False` | Whether to enable Xlite graph mode. Currently"
" only Llama, Qwen dense series models, and Qwen3-VL are supported. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enabled` | bool | `False` | 是否启用 Xlite 图模式。目前仅支持 Llama、Qwen 稠密系列模型和 "
"Qwen3-VL。 |"

msgid ""
"| `full_mode` | bool | `False` | Whether to enable Xlite for both the "
"prefill and decode stages. By default, Xlite is only enabled for the decode "
"stage. |"
msgstr ""
"| `full_mode` | bool | `False` | 是否为预填充和解码阶段均启用 Xlite。默认情况下，Xlite 仅对解码阶段启用。 "
"|"

msgid ""
"| `enabled`        | bool | `False`"
"                                                     | Whether to enable "
"weight prefetch. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enabled`        | bool | `False`"
"                                                     | 是否启用权重预取。 |"

msgid ""
"| `prefetch_ratio` | dict | `{\"attn\": {\"qkv\": 1.0, \"o\": 1.0}, \"moe\":"
" {\"gate_up\": 0.8}, \"mlp\": { \"gate_up\": 1.0,  \"down\": 1.0}}` | "
"Prefetch ratio of each weight.     |"
msgstr ""
"| `prefetch_ratio` | dict | `{\"attn\": {\"qkv\": 1.0, \"o\": 1.0}, \"moe\":"
" {\"gate_up\": 0.8}, \"mlp\": { \"gate_up\": 1.0,  \"down\": 1.0}}` | "
"每个权重的预取比例。     |"

msgid ""
"| `lmhead_tensor_parallel_size`    | int  | `0` | The custom tensor parallel"
" size of lm_head.    |"
msgstr ""
"| `lmhead_tensor_parallel_size`    | int  | `0` | lm_head 的自定义张量并行大小。    |"

msgid ""
"| `oproj_tensor_parallel_size`     | int  | `0` | The custom tensor parallel"
" size of o_proj.     |"
msgstr ""
"| `oproj_tensor_parallel_size`     | int  | `0` | o_proj 的自定义张量并行大小。     |"

msgid ""
"| `embedding_tensor_parallel_size` | int  | `0` | The custom tensor parallel"
" size of embedding. |"
msgstr ""
"| `embedding_tensor_parallel_size` | int  | `0` | embedding 的自定义张量并行大小。 |"

msgid ""
"| `mlp_tensor_parallel_size`       | int  | `0` | The custom tensor parallel"
" size of mlp.       |"
msgstr ""
"| `mlp_tensor_parallel_size`       | int  | `0` | mlp 的自定义张量并行大小。       |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_npugraph_ex`               | bool | `True` | Whether to enable "
"npugraph_ex backend.                                                 |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_npugraph_ex`               | bool | `True` | 是否启用 npugraph_ex 后端。"
"                                                 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_static_kernel` | bool | `False` | Whether to enable static kernel."
" Suitable for scenarios where shape changes are minimal and some time is "
"available for static kernel compilation. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_static_kernel` | bool | `False` | "
"是否启用静态内核。适用于形状变化较小且有时间进行静态内核编译的场景。 |"

msgid ""
"| `fuse_norm_quant`  | bool | `True` | Whether to enable fuse_norm_quant "
"pass. |"
msgstr "| `fuse_norm_quant`  | bool | `True` | 是否启用 fuse_norm_quant 优化。 |"

msgid ""
"| `fuse_qknorm_rope` | bool | `True` | Whether to enable fuse_qknorm_rope "
"pass. If Triton is not in the environment, set it to False. |"
msgstr ""
"| `fuse_qknorm_rope` | bool | `True` | 是否启用 fuse_qknorm_rope 优化。如果环境中没有 "
"Triton，请将其设置为 False。 |"

msgid ""
"| `fuse_allreduce_rms` | bool | `False` | Whether to enable "
"fuse_allreduce_rms pass. It's set to False because of conflict with SP. |"
msgstr ""
"| `fuse_allreduce_rms` | bool | `False` | 是否启用 fuse_allreduce_rms 优化。由于与 SP "
"冲突，默认设置为 False。 |"

msgid ""
"| `fuse_muls_add` | bool | `True` | Whether to enable fuse_muls_add pass.|"
msgstr "| `fuse_muls_add` | bool | `True` | 是否启用 fuse_muls_add 优化通道。|"

msgid ""
"| `dynamic_eplb`                   | bool| `False`| Whether to enable "
"dynamic EPLB. |"
msgstr "| `dynamic_eplb`                   | bool| `False`| 是否启用动态 EPLB。 |"

msgid ""
"| `expert_map_path`                | str | `None` | When using expert load "
"balancing for an MoE model, an expert map path needs to be passed in.|"
msgstr ""
"| `expert_map_path`                | str | `None` | 当对 MoE "
"模型使用专家负载均衡时，需要传入专家映射路径。|"

msgid ""
"| `expert_heat_collection_interval`| int | `400`  | Forward iterations when "
"EPLB begins. |"
msgstr ""
"| `expert_heat_collection_interval`| int | `400`  | EPLB 开始时的前向迭代次数。 |"

msgid ""
"| `algorithm_execution_interval`   | int | `30`   | The forward iterations "
"when the EPLB worker will finish CPU tasks. |"
msgstr ""
"| `algorithm_execution_interval`   | int | `30`   | EPLB 工作进程完成 CPU "
"任务时的前向迭代次数。 |"

msgid ""
"| `expert_map_record_path`         | str | `None` | Save the expert load "
"calculation results to a new expert table in the specified directory.|"
msgstr ""
"| `expert_map_record_path`         | str | `None` | "
"将专家负载计算结果保存到指定目录下的新专家表中。|"

msgid ""
"| `num_redundant_experts`          | int | `0`    | Specify redundant "
"experts during initialization. |"
msgstr "| `num_redundant_experts`          | int | `0`    | 在初始化时指定冗余专家数量。 |"

msgid ""
"| `eplb_policy_type`               | int | `1`    | EPLB balancing policy: "
"`0`=Random, `1`=DefaultEplb (open-source algorithm), `2`=SwiftBalanceEplb "
"(optimized for low-bandwidth), `3`=FlashLB (statistical method with sliding "
"windows). |"
msgstr ""
"| `eplb_policy_type`               | int | `1`    | EPLB "
"均衡策略：`0`=随机，`1`=DefaultEplb（开源算法），`2`=SwiftBalanceEplb（针对低带宽优化），`3`=FlashLB（基于滑动窗口的统计方法）。"
" |"

msgid ""
"| `eplb_heat_collection_stage`      | str | `\"all\"`| Stage to collect EPLB"
" heat: `\"prefill\"` collects only during prefill, `\"decode\"` collects "
"only during decode, `\"all\"` collects during both stages. In PD colocation "
"scenarios, prefill and decode requests may produce different expert "
"workloads. Selectively collecting heat on one stage can reduce expert "
"imbalance more effectively. |"
msgstr ""
"| `eplb_heat_collection_stage`      | str | `\"all\"`| 收集 EPLB "
"热度的阶段：`\"prefill\"` 仅在预填充阶段收集，`\"decode\"` 仅在解码阶段收集，`\"all\"` 在两个阶段都收集。在 PD "
"共置场景中，预填充和解码请求可能产生不同的专家负载。选择性地在某个阶段收集热度可以更有效地减少专家不均衡。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enabled`       | bool  | `False` | Whether to enable dynamic chunked "
"pipeline parallel. Requires `pipeline-parallel-size > 1`. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enabled`       | bool  | `False` | 是否启用动态分块流水线并行。需要 `pipeline-parallel-"
"size > 1`。 |"

msgid ""
"| `smooth_factor` | float | `1.0`   | Smoothing factor (0 < x ≤ 1.0). Higher"
" values trust the dynamic prediction more; `0.0` disables dynamic "
"adjustment. |"
msgstr ""
"| `smooth_factor` | float | `1.0`   | 平滑因子（0 < x ≤ 1.0）。值越大越信任动态预测；`0.0` "
"禁用动态调整。 |"

msgid ""
"| `min_chunk`     | int   | `4096`  | Minimum chunk size for dynamic "
"calculation. Should be smaller than `max-num-batched-tokens`. |"
msgstr ""
"| `min_chunk`     | int   | `4096`  | 动态计算的最小分块大小。应小于 `max-num-batched-"
"tokens`。 |"

msgid "| `need_timing` | bool | True | Enable/disable Online Calibration |"
msgstr "| `need_timing` | bool | True | 启用/禁用在线校准 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_block_verify`   | bool  | `False` | Whether to enable block verify"
" mode. Block verify evaluates all draft tokens as a block using cumulative "
"probability products, which can improve acceptance rate. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_block_verify`   | bool  | `False` | "
"是否启用块验证模式。块验证使用累积概率乘积将所有草稿令牌作为一个整体进行评估，可以提高接受率。 |"

msgid ""
"| `enable_entropy_verify` | bool  | `False` | Whether to enable entropy "
"verify mode. Entropy verify adjusts the acceptance threshold based on the "
"entropy of the target distribution — higher entropy (uncertain) tokens get a"
" lower threshold (easier to accept), while lower entropy (confident) tokens "
"get a stricter threshold. |"
msgstr ""
"| `enable_entropy_verify` | bool  | `False` | "
"是否启用熵验证模式。熵验证根据目标分布的熵调整接受阈值——熵较高（不确定）的令牌获得较低的阈值（更容易接受），而熵较低（确定）的令牌获得更严格的阈值。 "
"|"

msgid ""
"| `posterior_threshold`   | float | `0.95`  | Upper bound for the entropy-"
"adjusted acceptance threshold. Must be in (0, 1]. The effective threshold is"
" `min(exp(-entropy * posterior_alpha), posterior_threshold)`. |"
msgstr ""
"| `posterior_threshold`   | float | `0.95`  | 熵调整后接受阈值的上限。必须在 (0, 1] "
"范围内。有效阈值为 `min(exp(-entropy * posterior_alpha), posterior_threshold)`。 |"

msgid ""
"| `posterior_alpha`       | float | `0.4`   | Scaling factor for entropy in "
"the threshold computation. Must be >= 0. Higher values make the threshold "
"more sensitive to entropy — high-entropy tokens become much easier to "
"accept, improving performance but reducing precision. |"
msgstr ""
"| `posterior_alpha`       | float | `0.4`   | 阈值计算中熵的缩放因子。必须 >= "
"0。值越大，阈值对熵越敏感——高熵令牌变得更容易接受，从而提高性能但降低精度。 |"
